---
title: Lemongrass-Coconut Beef Noodle Soup with Snow Peas and Carrots
description: Inspired by the noodle soups served on the streets of Bangkok, this coconut beef noodle soup will warm your soul with each slurp. Fresh lemongrass and cilantro lend beautiful aromas to this bowl and each mouthful gets a satisfying crunch from crispy shallots.
